Company Overview of TVision Insights, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
TVision Insights, Inc. designs and develops a facial recognition technology to analyze television viewer behavior. It offers testing solutions to test creative concepts in audience’s living room; planning solutions to optimize media plans by demographic, daypart, channel, and program; and networking solutions to measure tune-in ads, product placement, and gain insights into audience behavior. TVision Insights, Inc. was incorporated in 2014 and is based in Cambridge, Massachusetts.


