Company







Overview



Overview








There was a problem loading your content.



Product


























Video










TVision Insights is a television attention measurement company pioneering the way brands, their agencies, TV networks and OTT platforms determine the true value of their video content and advertising. The company’s core technology uses data science and motion capture technology to passively assess “eyes on screen”, the single most accurate way to measure person-level engagement with video content.… · More Founded by two MIT alumni, TVision Insights is a venture-backed company headquartered in Boston, MA with offices in New York and Tokyo.






Founders







Yan Liu

CEO, Co-founder
Raised in China and grew up in both Japan and China. Yan started his career in McKinsey, then founded one of the leading digital agencies in Shanghai








Raymond Fu

CTO, Chief Scientist
Expert in artificial intelligence, big data, machine learning, and computer vision. Experience in both academic and industry. PhD of University of Illinois. 








Dan Schiffman

CRO
MIT Sloan MBA, GSD entrepreneur. Experience in going from concept to launch to growth. Expertise in SaaS, big data & eCommerce, building, marketing and selling.







